01:10:18.270 --> 01:10:19.170
I'm serious.

01:10:19.170 --> 01:10:21.970
By looking at prices,
you can tell the future.

01:10:21.970 --> 01:10:24.570
You can't do it
perfectly, but neither

01:10:24.570 --> 01:10:27.720
